</p>
<p>In other words, if we remove or add a <code>GenusScientist</code> from this array, it doesn't
make any difference! Doctrine ignores changes to the inverse side.</p>
<h2 id="setting-the-owning-side-by-reference">Setting the Owning Side: by_reference <a class="headerlink" href="collection-delete-orphan-removal#setting-the-owning-side-by-reference" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>How to fix it? We already know how! We did it back with our <code>ManyToMany</code> relationship!
It's a two step process.</p>
<p>First, in <code>GenusFormType</code>, set the <code>by_reference</code> option to <code>false</code>:</p>
