            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>For the last line, use <code>$genusScientist-&gt;setGenus(null)</code>. Let's update the note to say
the <em>opposite</em>:</p>
<blockquote><p>Needed to update the owning side of the relationship!</p>
</blockquote>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="c0dd522482">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
